  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 17th Level, you have learned to conjure the best version of your Shadow Hand which, by extension is the physical manifestation of your best self.</p><p>Your Shadowhand calculates its saving throws using your full Proficiency Bonus.</p><p>Also, you can now summon your Shadowhand at the start of your turn, at no action cost and when using its From the Ashes ability, it is resummoned with its full Hit Points.</p>",
